{"type":"message","id":"91cdc568","parentId":"3709eed1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:20:40.434Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fqkordti629e_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4257\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=0\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='the' new_len=0\n[master 0e0eea4] pulse: 2026-03-24 132016\n 5 files changed, 252 insertions(+), 148 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 132016.md\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 131914.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 132016 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFIxFreq scoring) as the next experiment. The scoring formula is now concrete: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). This needs to be implemented and tested against the 200-pulse dataset.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"marine-comet","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4257\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=0\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='the' new_len=0\n[master 0e0eea4] pulse: 2026-03-24 132016\n 5 files changed, 252 insertions(+), 148 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 132016.md\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 131914.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 132016 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFIxFreq scoring) as the next experiment. The scoring formula is now concrete: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120). This needs to be implemented and tested against the 200-pulse dataset.\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774372840433}}
