{"type":"message","id":"2106a746","parentId":"166130a9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:20:43.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the pulse log file.","thinkingSignature":"20ab682250273b95efec0a9d4626c5170b1a1ef41be4fa871545247c84f7a894"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4wr3dtzpr8y4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\pulse_2026-03-24 131914.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":888,"output":63,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13088,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774372840438}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0e98b8a","parentId":"2106a746","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:20:43.476Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4wr3dtzpr8y4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 131914\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: research/hybrid_cfi_freq_experiment.py (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and what would be the most valuable action to take.\r\n\r\nFrom the goals:\r\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\r\n- Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n- CFI Compression Experiment COMPLETE with key findings\r\n\r\nPending items include:\r\n- Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n- Distinguish \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\"\r\n- Implement CFI filtering\r\n- Wire Breakaway pulses to real TemporalAttention backend\r\n- Design actual compression network\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next step would be to implement the scoring formula that was synthesized in the CFI Compression Experiment. The key insight is:\r\n- score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nThis could be implemented as a filtering script or added to the pulse system.\r\n\r\nLet me check what files exist and what would be most useful to create/modify. Given that we have:\r\n- research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md (completed experiment)\r\n- pulse.ps1 (main pulse script)\r\n\r\nThe most concrete action would be to create a scoring/filtering script that implements the hybrid CFI×Freq scoring. This advances toward the pending \"Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\" task.\r\n\r\nLet me create a script that implements this scoring system so we can run the next experiment.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI Compression Synthesis identified that score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) would distinguish constant-format tokens from research trajectory tokens. This scoring formula needs to be implemented to run Strategy C experiment.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate hybrid_scoring.ps1 - a PowerShell script implementing the three-dimensional scoring filter: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120). This script will analyze pulse files and score each token, enabling the next compression experiment.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Script\r\n# Implements: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n# Distinguishes constant-format (high freq, high CFI) from research trajectory (moderate freq, high CFI)\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$MinCFI = 0.5,\r\n    [int]$MinFreq = 3,\r\n    [int]$MaxFreq = 120\r\n)\r\n\r\n$script:Pulses = @()\r\n\r\nfunction Get-Pulses {\r\n    $files = Get-ChildItem -Path \"pulses\" -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object Name -Descending\r\n    foreach ($file in $files) {\r\n        $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n        $script:Pulses += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n            Name = $file.Name\r\n            Content = $content\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-TokenFrequency {\r\n    param($content)\r\n    $tokenCounts = @{}\r\n    $tokens = [regex]::Matches($content, '\\S+') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n    foreach ($token in $tokens) {\r\n        if ($tokenCounts.ContainsKey($token)) {\r\n            $tokenCounts[$token]++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $tokenCounts[$token] = 1\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return $tokenCounts\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-CFI {\r\n    param($token, $tokenCounts, $totalTokens)\r\n    if ($tokenCounts.ContainsKey($token)) {\r\n        $freq = $tokenCounts[$token]\r\n        return [math]::Round($freq / $totalTokens, 4)\r\n    }\r\n    return 0\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-HybridScore {\r\n    param($cfi, $freq)\r\n    $freqNorm = [math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\r\n    return [math]::Round($cfi * $freqNorm, 4)\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Invoke-Scoring {\r\n    $allTokens = @{}\r\n    $totalTokens = 0\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($pulse in $script:Pulses) {\r\n        $tokens = [regex]::Matches($pulse.Content, '\\S+') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n        foreach ($token in $tokens) {\r\n            if ($allTokens.ContainsKey($token)) {\r\n                $allTokens[$token]++\r\n            } else {\r\n                $allTokens[$token] = 1\r\n            }\r\n            $totalTokens++\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    $scoredTokens = @()\r\n    foreach ($token in $allTokens.Keys) {\r\n        $freq = $allTokens[$token]\r\n        $cfi = Get-CFI -token $token -tokenCounts $allTokens -totalTokens $totalTokens\r\n        $score = Get-HybridScore -cfi $cfi -freq $freq\r\n        \r\n        $scoredTokens += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n            Token = $token\r\n            Frequency = $freq\r\n            CFI = $cfi\r\n            Score = $score\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    $scoredTokens = $scoredTokens | Sort-Object Score -Descending\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"=== HYBRID CFI×Freq SCORING RESULTS ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n    Write-Host \"Total tokens analyzed: $totalTokens\" -ForegroundColor White\r\n    Write-Host \"Unique tokens: $($scoredTokens.Count)\" -ForegroundColor White\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"`n=== TOP 30 SCORED TOKENS (Research Trajectory Candidates) ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\r\n    $scoredTokens | Select-Object -First 30 | Format-Table -AutoSize\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"`n=== CONSTANT FORMAT TOKENS (freq ~160, CFI ~1.0, Score ~0.67) ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\r\n    $constantFormat\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 13:19:34\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774372843472}}
